Performance, Low Cost, and Strong Security: Pick Any Three</a>” (<a
href="palmer-pick-any-3.pdf">local copy</a>) at the <a
href="http://www.web2expo.com/webexsf2009/public/schedule/speaker/1016">O’Reilly
Web 2.0 Expo 2009 conference</a>.</p>

<p>“<a
href="https://www.isecpartners.com/research/white-papers/secure-session-management-with-cookies-for-web-applications.aspx">Secure
Session Management With Cookies for Web Applications</a>” (<a
href="palmer-web-session-management.pdf">local copy</a>). There’s a few things
I’d change, now...</p>

<p>“<a href="iSEC-Breaking_Forensics_Software-Paper.v1_1.BH2007.pdf">Breaking
Forensics Software</a>”, with Alex Stamos and Tim Newsham.</p>
